*** 001 Fee Collection Initiation
*** 002 Fee Collection Response
** Message shape
*** Hdr (Header72, MsgFctn)
*** Acquirer (Acqrr)
*** Transaction id (TxId)
*** Transaction amounts (TxAmts)
